Package com.filestack.internal

Internal and utility classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseService
    Wraps endpoints that run on www.filestackapi.com.
    CdnService
    Wraps endpoints that run on cdn.filestackcontent.com.
    CloudService  
    UploadService
    Wraps endpoints that run on upload.filestackapi.com.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloudServiceUtil
    Functions to help create JSON bodies for Cloud API.
    HeaderInterceptor
    Intercepts requests to add Filestack headers.
    Networking
    Holds OkHttpClient and Retrofit singletons.
    ProgMapFunc  
    RetryNetworkFunc<T>
    Abstract class to generalize retry logic of a network call.
    Upload
    Holds upload state and request logic.
    UploadCompleteFunc
    Function to be passed to Flowable.fromCallable(Callable).
    UploadStartFunc
    Function to be passed to Flowable.fromCallable(Callable).
    UploadTransferFunc
    Function to be passed to Flowable.create(FlowableOnSubscribe, BackpressureStrategy).
    Util
    Small helper functions that don't need their own class.
